art troupes will be replaced with a system that will permit free 
and open competition among troupes performers will be allowed to 
set their own box office prices and decide their own programs as 
long as they are licensed and do not violate state laws and 
regulations 
wang said the reforms are designed to stimulate the professional 
enthusiam of the 200000 people working in the nations 3094 art 
troupes 
