campaign finance reporting law she herself is under investigation 
for omissions from her reports which she recently corrected 
if the trial begins as scheduled jury selection will start with 
distribution of a questionnaire designed to ferret out people with 
obvious bias 
for his part defense attorney scott said im confident that 
he should be acquitted but he added im not confident that it 
will happen 
